{%- comment -%}
  Internal links and assets use a ROOT-RELATIVE base_path (just the baseurl), so the
  site behaves identically on localhost and in production instead of jumping to the
  live domain during local preview. Fully-qualified URLs that genuinely need the host
  (SEO/canonical/Open Graph, the RSS feed, the sitemap) are produced separately via
  the `absolute_url` filter and `site.url`, so those remain absolute.
{%- endcomment -%}
{% assign base_path = site.baseurl %}